channel.title: Project Vildar (Jbirdscape)
channel.description:
[size=24pt]Project Vildar (Jbirdscape)[/size]
This is going to be a development team for the new upcoming server that needs to be coded quickly and put out. For a couple of reasons; many people waiting, this server needs to get big again, and i want it to. I also am a loyal owner. I have been procrastinating about this server the entire year of 2011. Thats bad, so if i have influential people and actual people that want it done rather than players that are just waiting and not asking. No, im not posting this so you can nag me. Im posting this for people/players who want to help develop this server with me, not in coding or programing wise. As in helping me with ideas, shaping this server for players. Not to the owners benefits. I dont want people who will just do this for staff, i want people that actually want to be in a server.
For you who dont know which is more than likely most of you, jbirdscape was a server made in october of 2006. It slowly grew, people started to play it alot, until multiple source changes and every one eventually quit. Then i renamed the server.
If you want to become part of this team please reply to this thread with information about you and why you want to join.
This team has no capacity of people. One reason being is because alot that sign up will not be loyal, they will just say so in about a week they will leave. If you dont have patience and dedication, please dont sign up.
When you sign up make sure you either have skype or msn. Skype preferrably.
- Dev Team - - Vildar (Jbird/Me) - - - - - -
